<subsection xml:id="subsec-real-life_problems_involving_data">
    <title>Real Life Problems Involving Data</title>

        <p>
            Applying the knowledge of data collection and organization to solve practical problems that students might encounter in their daily lives.
        </p>
    <activity>
        <p>
            <m>{\color{black} \textbf{Work in groups}}</m>
        </p>
        <p>
            <ol marker="a">
                <li>
                    <p>
                        Class Attendance: Collect the attendance of students in your class for one week. 
                        Organize the data and identify on which day(s) the attendance was highest and lowest. 
                    </p>
                </li>
                <li>
                    <p>
                        A shopkeeper keeps a record of the different sizes of school uniforms sold in a week. 
                        How can this data help the shopkeeper in the future?
                    </p>
                </li>
            </ol>
        </p>
    </activity>    
        
   </subsection>